# Obsidian vault (`notes/`)

The vault root is **`notes/`** at the repo root (gitignored). Open it in Obsidian alongside this project.

## Agent-only zone

All AI-generated notes go under **`notes/agents/`** only:

- Session logs: `notes/agents/sessions/`
- Plans: `notes/agents/cursor-plans/`
- Runbooks: `notes/agents/Cabinet PM/`

## Do not touch without explicit ask

- Human-maintained vault areas (if you use numbered folders like `00_Home/`, `99_Inbox/`, etc.)
- Do not add wikilinks from the main vault into `agents/` (one-way: agents reference code, not vice versa in Obsidian)

## Templates

Copy from `docs/vault-starter/` when bootstrapping. Session note template: `docs/vault-starter/agents/97_Templates/agent_session.md`

Setup guide: `docs/obsidian-vault.md`
